<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10127334>
    dc:description "Fig. 37. Xiphentedon acutigena sp. nov. A–B. ♀, holotype (Ivory Coast; CBGP). C–E. ♀♀, paratypes from Tanzania (C–D; CBGP) and RSA (E; SANC). F–H. ÔÔ, paratypes from DRC (F; MRAC) and from RSA (G–H; NHMUK). A, C, G. Habitus (inset C: axilla). B, D. Mesosoma and petiole. E–F. Face, the genal spike is arrowed. H. Head." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10127334/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10127338>
    dc:description "Fig. 38. Xiphentedon acutigena sp. nov. A. ♀, paratype (Ivory Coast; CBGP). B–E. Ô, paratype (RSA; NHMUK). A. Face. B. Head and anterior part of mesosoma. C. Prosternum. D. Propodeum. E. Axillula. The genal spike is arrowed in A and B." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10127338/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

